skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: vegan new orleans
des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in New Orleans, Louisiana. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Vegan New Orleans." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Vegan New Orleans for a suggestion."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
